    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts reliably, making it a dependable choice for daily driving. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections and light wear on the interior upholstery consistent with regular use, the overall appearance is clean and professional. It features a reliable infotainment system and comfortable seating, ensuring a pleasant experience for both driver and passengers. You can expect a solid, road-ready car that requires no immediate major repairs.",
