    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It\u2019s been my trusty companion and is still running like a champ! It's in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and carefully maintained, with just the usual character you\u2019d expect from a car that\u2019s actually been enjoyed. It's perfect for someone who wants a reliable, smooth ride without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
