    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul to ensure timing precision and long-term reliability. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and refreshed bushings throughout the suspension assembly. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed for peak performance, delivering the visceral feedback and balanced weight distribution this platform is renowned for.",
